Yearbook Committee</st>
<p>

The Yearbook Committee oversees and records various school run events, such as school dances, semi formals and spirit days, as  well as significant student achievements throughout the year. The committee is in charge of the entire creative and administrative process of the construction of the annual yearbook.</p>
<p>

The Editor-in-Chief of the Yearbook Committee for the 2008-2009 school year will be Kevan Lu.</p>

